      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/baby-products-retailer-firstcry-s-parent-set-to-debut-in-india-listing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[婴儿用品零售商 Brainbees Solutions Ltd. 的股价在交易首日上涨 46%，创下今年印度大型首次公开募股上市以来的最佳上市日涨幅。]]></description>
